Sales Dashboard Summary
This Sales Dashboard provides a clear and interactive overview of business performance using key metrics and insights. It features:

Profit by Year & Weekly Trends: Tracks sales profit over time to spot patterns and growth.

Customer & Product Profitability: Highlights top-performing customers and products, aiding in targeted strategy.

Percentage Profit Contribution: Shows each customer’s or product’s share of total profit.

Transaction Volume: Monitors sales activity across different periods.

Dynamic Formulas: Uses Excel functions to automate calculations, ensuring real-time accuracy.

Designed for quick insights and smarter decision-making, this dashboard supports better planning, performance tracking, and strategic focus.

